#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.diff.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.diff"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:1 of
msgid "Calculate the n-th discrete difference along the given axis."
msgstr "沿给定轴计算第 n 个离散差值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:3 of
msgid ""
"The first difference is given by ``out[n] = a[n+1] - a[n]`` along the "
"given axis, higher differences are calculated by using `diff` "
"recursively."
msgstr ""
"第一个差值由 ``out[n] = a[n+1] - a[n]`` 沿给定轴给出，更高的差值通过递归"
"使用 `diff` 计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:7 of
msgid "Input tensor"
msgstr "输入张量"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:9 of
msgid ""
"The number of times values are differenced. If zero, the input is "
"returned as-is."
msgstr "差分的次数。如果为零，则按原样返回输入。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:12 of
msgid "The axis along which the difference is taken, default is the last axis."
msgstr "进行差分的轴，默认是最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:16 of
msgid ""
"**diff** -- The n-th differences. The shape of the output is the same as "
"`a` except along `axis` where the dimension is smaller by `n`. The type "
"of the output is the same as the type of the difference between any two "
"elements of `a`. This is the same as the type of `a` in most cases. A "
"notable exception is `datetime64`, which results in a `timedelta64` "
"output tensor."
msgstr ""
"**diff** -- 第 n 个差值。输出的形状与 `a` 相同，除了在 `axis` 轴上维度会"
"减少 `n`。输出类型与 `a` 中任意两个元素之间差值的类型相同。在大多数情况下"
"，这与 `a` 的类型一致。一个显著的例外是 `datetime64` 类型，其结果为 `"
"timedelta64` 输出张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`gradient`, :py:obj:`ediff1d`, :py:obj:`cumsum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:27 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:28 of
msgid ""
"Type is preserved for boolean tensors, so the result will contain `False`"
" when consecutive elements are the same and `True` when they differ."
msgstr ""
"布尔张量的类型会被保留，因此当连续元素相同时结果将包含 `False`，不同时则"
"为 `True`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:32 of
msgid ""
"For unsigned integer tensors, the results will also be unsigned. This "
"should not be surprising, as the result is consistent with calculating "
"the difference directly:"
msgstr ""
"对于无符号整数张量，结果也将是无符号的。这并不令人意外，因为结果与直接"
"计算差值是一致的："

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:44 of
msgid ""
"If this is not desirable, then the array should be cast to a larger "
"integer type first:"
msgstr "如果这不可取，则应首先将数组转换为更大的整数类型："

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.diff.diff:52 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

